    Advanced Shaman UI Library Rewrite
    Features:
    - Draggable window
    - Resizable window with grip
    - Minimize / Close
    - Global toggle keybind to open/close UI
    - Settings panel
    - Config save/load (flags + window state + theme + keybind)
    - Cleaner visuals / gradients / shadows / rounded styling
    - Better architecture for extending controls

    Notes:
    - This is a rewrite focused on the requested core framework features.
    - It keeps Roblox exploit-style APIs where possible (writefile, isfile, makefolder, etc.).
    - Replace callbacks / add more widgets as needed.
]]

